# Fleet runtime state — do not commit
# These files are written by both feature-branch builds AND base-branch
# validator runs. Tracking them in git causes merge conflicts on every
# PR merge.

# Operational logs (timestamps, dispatch events, raw script output)
logs/*.log
logs/METRICS.md
logs/GRAVEYARD.md

# Kill switch (presence-only; never committed)
KILL_SWITCH

# macOS junk
.DS_Store

# Local-only files an operator might create during debugging
*.local.bak
*.tmp
